      • disabled

        public RestCallLoggerConfig.Builder disabled(Enablement value)
        Enables no-trace mode on this config.

        No-trace mode prevents logging of messages to the log file.

        Possible values (case-insensitive):

        • TRUE - No-trace mode enabled for all requests.
        • FALSE - No-trace mode disabled for all requests.
        • PER_REQUEST - No-trace mode enabled for requests that have a "X-NoTrace: true" header.
        Parameters:
        value - The value for this property.
        Can be null (inherit from parent or default to NEVER).
        Returns:
        This object (for method chaining).
